'''Akarere ka Polatlı ''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Polatlı ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere ka Polatlı ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 110.990 (abagabo 56.120 n’abagore 54.870)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 3465,81 .

== Akarere gahana imbibe ==
Gahana imbibi na:
:Mu majyaruguru :  Akarere ka [[Beypazarı]], Akarere k’[[Ayaş]] n’Akarere ka [[Sincan]] 
:Mu burasirazuba : Akarere ka [[Yenimahalle]], Akarere ka [[Gölbaşı]] n’Akarere ka [[Haymana]] 
:Mu majyepfo : [[Intara ya Konya]]
:Mu burengerazuba : [[Intara y’Eskişehir]]

